Dialogue.Value: Ah，you must be a tourist!,I know since you came from,that warp over there.
Engelles’ Internet is pretty,complex. Keep your eyes,peeled so you don't get lost.
In Japan，isn’t the road to the,Square called the Main Street?
We don’t have anything like,that here in Engelles Area.
I’M THE MATRON SPRITE,OF KINDNESS〜! THE,SQUARE IS THIS WAY〜!
BUT IF YOU TAKE THE,WARP，YOU’LL GO TO,AREA 2! HAVE FUN〜!
ALL SPRITES ARE TRAINED,TO SPEAK MULTIPLE,LANGUAGES!
This part of the Net was ,deliberately designed to be,confusing， believe it or not!
Back when the Cyberworld,Theory came over from Japan，,lots of folks didn’t trust the idea.
So they thought: Let’s connect，,but make it as tough to navigate,as we can! Data’ll find the way!
Turns out viruses are data too，,and all that did was make things,harder for everyone else.
Oh no.....,I swear I took the right warp to,the Square....
You just can’t trust anyone on,the Net these days，especially,not based on how they look!
Some creeps choose “Child”-,type Navis just to trick people!,Ugh!
Are you sure there’s no beach,Net around here? Port Engelles,is 10 minutes away，tops.
I’m quite sure. Engelles Net,represents the city proper，,and this is no beach town.
Aww.... I smelled an ocean,breeze somewhere，now all I,want is to go to the beach....
